title.narrative: Revenue Administration and Revenue Policy - Zambia. Revenue Policy and Administration - Zambia

description.narrative: Support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy, most importantly financial intermediation – the efficient generation and allocation of savings to their most productive use.

This award strives to support the establishment of a sound private, well-functioning, equitable financial sector that fulfills critical roles in a market economy. More specifically, this includes Assistance to the Zambia Revenue Authority (ZRA) includes (1) reengineering debt management activities; 2) designing a program to increase corporate and employee productivity; 3) establishing a robust and structured appeals process for audit and customs; 4) strengthening internal affairs operational capability; 5) enhancing outreach for taxpayer education; 6) streamlining customs operations through the use of risk management; and 7) supporting criminal investigation division.. Project was a one time training event..
